dutta vs dutta is a 2012 indian bengali film directed by anjan dutt .   this is anjan dutt 's semi-autobiographical film .   most of the film has been shot in a house of amherst street in kolkata .   anjan has described this house resonated feel of his old house of beniapukur . the film received positive reviews .   according to anandabazar patrika reviewer sangeeta bandopadhyay , this was anjan dutt 's best film .   this opinion has been supported by another bengali newspaper ei samay too .